  "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>Content Warning </i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i>This game contains depictions of blood and violence (including vampire bites), depression, and suicide.</i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Velvet Bite:  Softly, With Teeth</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >ベルベット·バイト / 轻咬丝绒 / 벨벳 바이트</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Romance with Vampires</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You've been invited to a Halloween party! Yay!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Music! Food! Drinks! Vampires!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Wait. VAMPIRES!?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A Romantic Visual Novel</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >featuring 6 romanceable vampires.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Main Routes</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Madison</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/4e0631013a4859ed428eaf2aa5a94c39.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>    That's my question to ask.</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Why are you here?</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Your roommate! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She's not happy to be around you, obviously.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Kojyo Rin / Lee Jueun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Forrest</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/b4166ecfdae52d3864d5a118e0ed17db.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <i><u>City life isn't good for your mental health.</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Vampires also need greens to heal.</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Kind and caring. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >His dessert wasn't very good. Too bad.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Hozuki Kaoru / Shim Gyuhyuk</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Yvonne</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/6daf907ddf24d521f50657bedf1b222e.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Hm, what's good for a fairy?</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>Cutie pie? Or sweetheart?</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A beauty, known to never age. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Runs a business.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Uduki Hana / Kim Jayeon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Sebastian</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/1c5ff1a64c50109c55e888a4ae1e0049.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>I mistook you for a different person.</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>I guess I was drunk.</u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Book lover and movie enthusiast. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Not a social person.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Utamaru / Seok Seunghoon</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u></u></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Bonus Routes</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Charlotte</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/ffdcaa05f0f1b7624ddadba05a28344a.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><i>    So, was the party worth it?</i></u> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Your psychiatrist.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >She's also a vampire, by the way.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Masutani Mahiro / Yang Jeonghwa</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>Everard</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2894820/extras/7521c8a9fcbfc0f5ef1361dd1a8cc326.avif?t=1739535910\" width=500 height=500 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>    Only do the fun stuff. </u></i></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><i><u>    That's my life philosophy.</u></i> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Is he a magician or a con artist? </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >We don't know.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >CV. Wakanae Yoi / Kim Youngsun</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Features</u></strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>#vampire #halloween #pastel </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>#choices-matter #text-based #romance </strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>#josei #joseimuke #LGBTQ+ #amare</strong> </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💘 Name your Main Character </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💘 Beautiful Art</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >💘 Original Soundtrack<br><strong>💘</strong> Voice Acting</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong><u>Play Time</u></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >9~12 hours (estimated, depending on the player's reading speed)</p>",
